{"word":"H2946 - טָפַח - ṭâphach - taw-fakh' - Span","slug":"H2946","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">טָפַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ṭâphach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>taw-fakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Span"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D8;&#x05E4;&#x05D7; - t&#x0323;a&#x0302;phach</b> - <i>taw-fakh'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>flatten</i> out or <i>extend</i> (as a tent); figuratively to <i>nurse</i> a child (as <i>promotive</i> of growth); or perhaps a denominative from <a href=\"#/H2947\">H2947</a>, from <i>dandling</i> on the palms: - span, swaddle."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2947\">H2947</a>, <a href=\"#/H2948\">H2948</a>, <a href=\"#/H2949\">H2949</a>, <a href=\"#/H4304\">H4304</a>"}]}